jebcarter/psyonic-cetacean-20B.description: Older but extremely creative model that does well across a wide range of tasks but has some drawbacks. extremely high KV context size, being near 6gb per 4k context, and below average intelegence compared to modern models that will use the same memory. Alpaca RP focused model that excels across many tasks. Generally fairly reliable even outside of RP.

THUDM/GLM-Z1-Rumination-32B-0414.name: THUDM/GLM-Z1-Rumination-32B-0414
THUDM/GLM-Z1-Rumination-32B-0414.description: Based on GLM-4-32B-0414, which is comparable in performance to OpenAI GPT series and DeepSeek V3/R1 series, GLM-Z1-Rumination-32B-0414 is a deep reasoning model with rumination capabilities (similar to OpenAI's Deep Research). Unlike typical deep thinking models, the rumination model employs longer periods of deep thought to solve more open-ended and complex problems. The rumination model integrates search tools during its deep thinking process to handle complex tasks. Z1-Rumination shows significant improvements in research-style writing and complex retrieval tasks. (Some capabilities may not be available on the AI Horde).
